# 🌟 Store Rating Web App

A full-stack rating platform where users can rate stores, store owners can view their feedback, and admins can manage users and stores. Designed with mobile users in mind.

---

## 📁 Project Structure

```

store-rating-app/
├── backend/         # Node.js + Express + JSON-based API
├── frontend/        # React.js UI
├── README.md        # Project documentation

````

---

## 🚀 Getting Started

### 🔧 Backend Setup

```bash
cd backend
npm install
node index.js
````

* Runs on: `http://localhost:7000`
* Uses file-based storage (`users.json`, `stores.json`, `rating.json`)

---

### 🌐 Frontend Setup

```bash
cd frontend
npm install
npm start
```

* Runs on: `http://localhost:3000`
* Built with React and Bootstrap

---

## 👤 User Roles & Features

### 👥 Normal User

* Register & login
* View stores and their average ratings
* Submit and edit store ratings (1–5 stars)

### 🏪 Store Owner

* Login
* View users who rated their store
* View their store’s average rating

### 🛠️ System Administrator

* Login to dashboard
* Add users (Normal/Admin) and stores
* View all users and their roles
* View all stores and submitted ratings

---

## 🌟 Key Features

* Responsive & mobile-friendly UI
* Star rating component with edit confirmation
* Role-based routing & access control
* JSON file-based backend (no database required)
* Clean, styled interface using Bootstrap

